Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(850,850)\pos(160,380)\fnSimSun\fs30}第二話 潛航極限
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.68,0:00:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躍遷立場？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.06,0:00:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.89,0:00:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聾了嗎 開始炮擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.73,0:00:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敵艦的瞄準鐳射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.47,0:00:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦艦尾已被鎖定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.03,0:00:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大輸出功率 起航準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴魯丹諾斯 起航
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向下45度 急速潛航
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.32,0:01:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿度亞的船 居然可以潛沙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受強脈衝磁場的影響 產生了電磁干擾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去目標蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止給電子室供應等離子體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀測班迅速用肉眼確認情況
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沙塵的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可見光和遠紅外線都難以捕捉到敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方沙地有內聚力崩潰反應
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是擬似相變立場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,QTF嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 第三類戒備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對潛艦模式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲納員 展開聲納陣列
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在LS界面相完全沉沒之前抓住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲納陣列 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陣列啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不只是潛沙那麼簡單呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深度300 界面相潛行中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前 船內的損壞情況無異常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有被追蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三艘艦船的鍋爐音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從左舷後方接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然在他們眼前消失所以慌了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倆舷的鍋爐熄火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長 他們的鍋爐音...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是想拖住我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來敵人多半是懂沙戰的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 他們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在垂釣等我們上鉤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦 進入第四就緒狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解 主鍋爐 倆舷減速
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倆舷微速
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍋爐噪音降至60分貝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2號“獵犬”沒能確認目標船隻的聲紋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擴大1和3號“獵犬”的搜索範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是摒起氣息藏起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在強化榴彈上裝上延遲信管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向目標船隻的潛航地點前方1000米處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以散佈角度5度的散點爆炸方式發射
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有動靜了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是發射音 他們打過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 準備迎接衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸彈的位置別聽錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 薩姆 你也來幫幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小貓咪 乖乖呆著別動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸地點 前方1000米
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然他們只是在瞎蒙而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢 這不是攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過剛才的爆炸 他們確認了我們的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 30方向 兩舷微速前進
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩舷微速前進
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到目標回音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯示到1號屏幕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干擾紋波上觀測到內聚力崩潰的群延時特性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然目標展開了擬似相變立場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LS界面相的半徑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約120米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想像中的要大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界面相移動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30方向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲紋消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用非線性預測濾波器繼續追蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給垂直發射系統裝上沙錨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要用沙錨進行攻擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於沙中的敵人 激光槍沒有絲毫作用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那樣的話瑪雅大人她...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前最重要的是把目標留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我負全責
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝填沙錨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1357號垂直發射系統 裝填錨杆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈道瞄準 鎖定LS界面相的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準 修正誤差
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙錨能量注入完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時可以發射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙錨 發射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦的發射音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4發 6發 越來越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是發射深沙炸彈了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 如果是深沙炸彈 撞擊聲會更小一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播放發射音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射音 播放中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倆舷全速 右滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要衝進岩礁地帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管 繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動主動聲納
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 上面那些人...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 岩礁是很好的掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動主動聲納
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脈衝？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11點方向傳來脈衝的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是主動聲納
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出音源的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回音？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右舷30度 鑽到3號和5號的中間去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷兩倍速 右舷30度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.91,0:09:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別叫 在幹著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右舷45度 繞到5號那邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右舷45度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用多普勒差分濾波器 把那艘船給我挖出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿過5號了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12點方向 不規則岩礁6號
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倆舷停止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍋爐 全力急停
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準 最終調整
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將數據傳送到沙錨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙錨 突入沙底
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上方有衝擊音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙錨的回音 捕捉到未知的衝擊波
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.93,0:11:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方區域的粒子穴也已恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.57,0:11:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LS界面相消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是抓到目標了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電磁干渉波有什麼反應
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前還沒有觀測到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉失敗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我想像中還要有兩手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上確認損傷狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎聲停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不是什麼東西被破壞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 瑪雅 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大夫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米梅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快抬她到醫務室去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人到底...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是停止了擬似相變立場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏在沙中 能讓沙錨的威力大打折扣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不展開LS界面相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩礁就是很好的掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大大降低了被聲納發現的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍋爐室的管道受到一定程度的破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷後方出現裂縫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在亞穆正前往維修
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量子躍遷引擎什麼時候再啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沙裏面 很難排熱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦內的溫度 以及對艦艇的壓力 都...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們應該知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是在潛沙那麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來敵人很有頭腦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長 這樣下去撐不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群傢夥繼續坐在那裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊吧 還能勉強把魚雷從這裡發射到地面去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘記了我們還沒來得及取得補給嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射管裏面只剩下兩枚魚雷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使全部命中 敵人還有一艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這樣妥當嗎 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅大人就在敵艦上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脈搏很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米梅 注射3號藥水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我拿水來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.23,0:14:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船內溫度超過了45度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦內的溫度即將超過界限
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是那樣 瑪雅大人...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 會撐不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船內溫度 48度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船內溫度 即將超過50度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船...船長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦 微速後退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此回航
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量子躍遷引擎 啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上浮至潛望鏡深度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:16:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復了恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一群沒耐性的傢夥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你什麼都沒幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛嚷得那麼大聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫什麼都沒幹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又扇扇子 又端水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我覺得這純粹是在礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒礙事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,475)\fnSimSun\fad(840,0)\fs25}Theseus總部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:18:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下等人拿度亞的沙賊船 居然能潛沙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是下屬小看了拿度亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群可惡的傢夥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是太過縱容他們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.22,0:19:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要給點苦頭他們吃才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅大人為何想從我們的保護之下逃跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她身處的時間和空間都跟我們不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人能瞭解她的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當她的保姆實在是當膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此 對我們來說 她是必不可缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 屬下定會將她帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒什麼時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸一下新鮮空氣 心情也會開朗一點的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我有好東西 跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.40,0:20:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白娜絲 我進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還納悶著今天是個什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:20:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟平時沒什麼兩樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.46,0:21:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩姆帶回來那個女孩子的病歷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治療的時候有點在意 就去查了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可不是一般人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Theseus那些傢夥 為什麼盯上我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.72,0:23:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳言薩姆帶回來的那個女孩子會帶來厄運
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.83,0:23:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這話 小心薩姆跑來揍你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.26,0:23:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對面已經打起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.89,0:23:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也插一腳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,300)\fnSimSun\fs30}第三話 「千年的迷惑」
